quran[30]{c,v,t}:
  78,1,"Ko …ìee sirku…ìe naamnandirta caggal de Alla neli e mum en nelaa…óo Makko-yo o his-"
  78,2,"Ho…ìe naamnandira kabaaru maw…óo on, oon woni Quraana teddu…óo tellinaa…óo e nelaa…óo mum en coom…óo kabaaru ummital."
  78,3,"O Quraana mbo …ìe luuri e mum e ko…ìe cifatoo mbo ko, wonde kombo mbilewu wolla jime wollo wageyaagal wolla tinndi adii…ìe."
  78,4,"Wonah no…ìe ngaa∆¥arii nih, …ìee fennu…ìe qurana ma…ìe nganndu batte pennugol ma…ì…ìe bonngol."
  78,5,"Refti teentana …ìe …óuum."
  78,6,"Mbela Min mbattaani leydi ndi keblaandi wonande …ìe, lobbundi ngam √±ii…ìal mum en."
  78,7,"Min mba…ói pelle …óe pen…óe na ha…óa leydi ndi dimmbaade."
  78,8,"Min tagi on onon yim…ìe nooneeli: wor…ìe e rew…ìe."
  78,9,"Min mba…ói …óoyngol mon ta∆¥aade gah e golle ngam poofta…óon."
  78,10,"Min mba…ói jemma o ko cuuroowo on hono ni…ìe jemma mbo cuurdaton awraali mon."
  78,11,"Min mba…ói √±alawma o lefu faggitaade e yiilaade arsuka."
  78,12,"Min mahi dow mon kammuuli jee…ói…ói cattu…ói mahnga √±ee√±u…ói gollal."
  78,13,"Min mba…ói naange nge lampu cattu…óa ku…ì…ìam e njalbeendi."
  78,14,"Min tellini ummaade e duule pot…óe to…ìde ndiyam njuppajam sanne."
  78,15,"Ngam Min yaltina heen noone gabbe, e noone pu…ói."
  78,16,"Min njaltina heen gese pilandir…óe le…ì…ó…ó ngam naatandirde cate mum."
  78,17,"Pellet, √±alawma ceerndugol hakkunde tagaa…óe laatiima ko ka dotta e waktu mbo luutndataako."
  78,18,"√ëande Malayka o wutti e allaadu he wuttannde …óimmere, ngaron-onon yim…ìe- pelle pelle."
  78,19,"Kammu on uddite mbo wonta hono dame udditaa…óe."
  78,20,"Pelle …óe mba…óaa jahooje haa …óe ngonti punndi nduuyndi, …óe mba*i hono merere."
  78,21,"Pellet yiite jahannama nge wontii tommbii nge."
  78,22,"Nge wonanii bew…ìe …ìe ruttorde ka…ìe nduttato."
  78,23,"…ìe √±ii…ìa toon yontaaji …ói ngalah happu."
  78,24,"…ìe mee…óatah toon henndu …ìuu…ìndu ustooru nguli Sa*iir, wonah ndiyam …ìuu…ì…óam kono dakmitire."
  78,25,"…ìe mee…óatah si wonah ndiyam ngul…óam jaw, e ∆¥ii∆¥iiri ciiwatoondi e yim…ìe yiite."
  78,26,"Njobdi yaadundi e ko…ìe wonno ko e dow mum ummaade e keefeeru e majjere."
  78,27,"Pellet …ìe e aduna …ìe kulaano haasboore Alla ka laakira, sabu …ìe ngoon…óinaani ummital, si…ìe ngoon…óinna ummital …ìe ngoon…óinatna Alla, …ìe golla ko mo∆¥∆¥i."
  78,28,"…ìe penni aayeeje Amen tellinaa…óe e Nelaa…óo Amen pennugol."
  78,29,"Kala huunde e golle mum en Min tonnggi…óe Min limi, tawa na winnda e …óeri golle mum en."
  78,30,"Mee…óe -onon bewbe- …óee lepte duumii…óe, Min …ìeydantah on si wonah lepte e dow lepte mon."